snippet.title: LOFI Katana | Official Trailer | Coming Soon
snippet.description:
Hey everyone,

We are very proud to present you the official trailer of LOFI Katana.
Coming in July 2023 !

We would be very thankful if you could add it to your wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1723680/LOFI_Katana/

Feel free to join our discord, we would be happy to discuss with you !
https://discord.gg/f4Jpnzpwen

Take care :)

Follow us on our other socials
https://www.instagram.com/lofi.katana
https://twitter.com/LofiKatana
https://www.tiktok.com/@lofi.katana

Music: Bad Snacks - A Caring Friend
